// start with the hardest thing (attempt at the next progression, bad form = 100%),
// then negatives-into-holds, dynamic straight-arm work, touches, activation. Strength
// skills get the three day types (intense A / volume C / recovery B). Coordination
// skills run high frequency, low intensity. A skeleton — autoregulate. Credited to Anton.
